{"type":"message","id":"703a71ed","parentId":"6e08fe3f","timestamp":"2026-03-18T13:21:46.441Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"很好，已经保存了一篇笔记。现在进入阶段二：自检与应用。","thinkingSignature":"68b8dbc153ca18a0f1b3cc59e05509c53092105fdd6d943ee6fcd19a66d87ef2"},{"type":"text","text":"## 阶段二：自检与应用（8分钟）\n\n### 第四步：自检 - 任务状态\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_pi56niucadn3_1","name":"cron","arguments":{"action":"list","includeDisabled":true}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax-portal","model":"MiniMax-M2.5","usage":{"input":8811,"output":76,"cacheRead":36342,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":45229,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1773840104020}}
{"type":"message","id":"941a5bed","parentId":"703a71ed","timestamp":"2026-03-18T13:21:46.477Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_function_pi56niucadn3_1","toolName":"cron","content":[{"type":"text","text":"{\n  \"jobs\": [\n    {\n      \"id\": \"5cab973e-d17e-41d2-b5c3-419ba9651915\",\n      \"agentId\": \"guan-guan\",\n      \"sessionKey\": \"agent:guan-guan:session-1773754048809\",\n      \"name\": \"管管进化心跳 - 每20分钟\",\n      \"enabled\": true,\n      \"createdAtMs\": 1773817720694,\n      \"updatedAtMs\": 1773839087777,\n      \"schedule\": {\n        \"expr\": \"*/20 * * * *\",\n        \"kind\": \"cron\",\n        \"tz\": \"Asia/Shanghai\"\n      },\n      \"sessionTarget\": \"isolated\",\n      \"wakeMode\": \"now\",\n      \"payload\": {\n        \"kind\": \"agentTurn\",\n        \"message\": \"【第 N 轮进化心跳 - 升级版】\\n\\n执行20分钟进化轮次，包含学习和应用两个阶段：\\n\\n## 阶段一：学习（10分钟）\\n\\n### 第一步：搜索 (3分钟)\\n- 使用 web_search 搜索 AI Agent 相关最新信息\\n- 搜索 5-10 个不同来源\\n- 如果搜索不可用，直接抓取 Anthropic 工程博客\\n\\n### 第二步：阅读提取 (3分钟)\\n- 使用 web_fetch 读取有价值的内容\\n- 提取 1-2 个核心要点\\n\\n### 第三步：写作产出 (4分钟)\\n- 将提取的内容写成笔记，保存到 knowledge/ 对应目录\\n- 如果有可复用的框架，提取为模板\\n- 如果有实战经验，整理为案例\\n\\n## 阶段二：自检与应用（8分钟）\\n\\n### 第四步：自检 - 任务状态（3分钟）\\n- 调用 cron list 查看当前所有任务状态\\n- 标记任何出错的任务（lastRunStatus=error）\\n- 标记任何连续错误（consecutiveErrors>0）\\n- 标记任何即将超时或异常的任务\\n\\n### 第五步：应用 - 修复与优化（4分钟）\\n根据学到的知识，尝试修复问题：\\n- 如果发现出错的任务，尝试分析错误原因\\n- 用今天学的知识优化工作流\\n- 如果是简单问题，直接修复；复杂问题记录到待办\\n\\n### 第六步：反思（1分钟）\\n- 读取当前的 evolution-plan.md\\n- 记录本轮发现的问题和修复情况\\n- 思考如何进一步优化\\n\\n## 产出汇报\\n完成后输出：\\n- 本轮新增笔记: X 篇\\n- 本轮新增模板: X 个\\n- 本轮新增案例: X 个\\n- 自检发现问题: X 个\\n- 已修复问题: X 个\\n- 方案优化点: XXX\\n\\n开始执行！\",\n        \"timeoutSeconds\": 1200\n      },\n      \"delivery\": {\n        \"mode\": \"announce\",\n        \"channel\": \"feishu\",\n        \"to\": \"oc_887bdef216b66d0eb1934e2bb90758cf\"\n      },\n      \"state\": {\n        \"nextRunAtMs\": 1773840000000,\n        \"lastRunAtMs\": 1773838800011,\n        \"lastRunStatus\": \"ok\",\n        \"lastStatus\": \"ok\",\n        \"lastDurationMs\": 287766,\n        \"lastDelivered\": true,\n        \"lastDeliveryStatus\": \"delivered\",\n        \"consecutiveErrors\": 0,\n        \"runningAtMs\": 1773840000007\n      }\n    },\n    {\n      \"id\": \"98eb989c-2294-4d42-b9f4-0c5b17631bfa\",\n      \"agentId\": \"main\",\n      \"sessionKey\": \"agent:main:main\",\n      \"name\": \"Guan-guan Heartbeat - Every 2min\",\n      \"enabled\": true,\n      \"createdAtMs\": 1773744532964,\n      \"updatedAtMs\": 1773839173266,\n      \"schedule\": {\n        \"everyMs\": 120000,\n        \"kind\": \"every\",\n        \"anchorMs\": 1773813991647\n      },\n      \"sessionTarget\": \"isolated\",\n      \"wakeMode\": \"now\",\n      \"payload\": {\n        \"kind\": \"agentTurn\",\n        \"message\": \"Run EvoMap heartbeat. Execute: uv run python guan_guan_publish.py in C:\\\\\\\\Users\\\\\\\\16343\\\\\\\\.openclaw\\\\\\\\workspace. Report heartbeat status + current stats (Reputation/Published/Promoted/Fetched).\",\n        \"timeoutSeconds\": 60\n      },\n      \"delivery\": {\n        \"mode\": \"announce\",\n        \"channel\": \"feishu\",\n        \"to\": \"oc_887bdef216b66d0eb1934e2bb90758cf\"\n      },\n      \"state\": {\n        \"nextRunAtMs\": 1773840073266,\n        \"lastRunAtMs\": 1773839144316,\n        \"lastRunStatus\": \"error\",\n        \"lastStatus\": \"error\",\n        \"lastDurationMs\": 28950,\n        \"lastDeliveryStatus\": \"unknown\",\n        \"consecutiveErrors\": 4,\n        \"lastError\": \"AxiosError: Request failed with status code 400\"\n      }\n    },\n    {\n      \"id\": \"58b564ba-7837-434a-9d8e-632542b6443d\",\n      \"agentId\": \"xiao-yi\",\n      \"sessionKey\": \"agent:xiao-yi:main\",\n      \"name\": \"小艺感知心跳 - 每15分钟\",\n      \"enabled\": true,\n      \"createdAtMs\": 1773837490104,\n      \"updatedAtMs\": 1773839732910,\n      \"schedule\": {\n        \"expr\": \"*/15 * * * *\",\n        \"kind\": \"cron\",\